        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Ban Corporate PACs Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits for-profit corporations from establishing a separate segregated political fund. Existing funds must terminate and disburse their entire balance not later than one year after the enactment of this bill.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
